{"tid":144934,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"34E陳偉琪胸襲馬場　死黐神秘男子！","createTime":"2017-03-06T00:00:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T13:19:53.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"727f3b33de952ac677c580ebe01ccfb5dc29cd23","tid":144934,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:00:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170305/photo/bkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_01b.jpg?20170306071236\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170305%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20170306071236&h=fa5fa088&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嘩嘩嘩&hellip;望邊好呀？<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170305/photo/bkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_02b.jpg?20170306071236\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170305%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20170306071236&h=a24109a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳偉琪（左二）表現勁風騷。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170305/photo/bkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_03b.jpg?20170306071236\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170305%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20170306071236&h=23646c87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳偉琪仲露埋背，真係離遠都見到佢。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170305/photo/bkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_04b.jpg?20170306071236\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170305%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20170306071236&h=127c5bf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳偉琪同戴帽嘅護花男超好傾。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170305/photo/bkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_05b.jpg?20170306071236\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170305%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20170306071236&h=93593ed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咬晒唇諗緊乜呀？<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170305/photo/bkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_06b.jpg?20170306071236\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170305%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20170306071236&h=cb4797ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳偉琪對鏡頭都幾敏感。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170305/photo/bkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_07b.jpg?20170306071236\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170305%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_07b.jpg%3F20170306071236&h=4a62f2d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n視覺效果震撼。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170305/photo/bkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_08b.jpg?20170306071236\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170305%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_08b.jpg%3F20170306071236&h=a977f911&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日係暖咗少少嘅。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170305/photo/bkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_09b.jpg?20170306071236\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170305%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_09b.jpg%3F20170306071236&h=28529c36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳偉琪講起護花男（左）勁緊張，仲再三強調只係朋友關係。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170305/photo/bkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_10b.jpg?20170306071236\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170305%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_10b.jpg%3F20170306071236&h=def155a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家明嘅、明嘅！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170305/photo/bkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_11b.jpg?20170306071236\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170305%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_11b.jpg%3F20170306071236&h=5fd43086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳偉琪孖住護花男滿場飛。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170305/photo/bkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_12b.jpg?20170306071236\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170305%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_12b.jpg%3F20170306071236&h=07ca99ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一齊應酬吓。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170305/photo/bkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_13b.jpg?20170306071236\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170305%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001_13b.jpg%3F20170306071236&h=86effc89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係形影不離。<br />\n<br />\n馬場今天明星眾多，擁有34E上圍的無綫新一代咪神陳偉琪亦有現身，她的身旁還出現了一位戴帽護花男，問到是否新男友？她卻否認二人是拍拖：「唔好誤會，佢係Family Friend嚟㗎，我Uncle有愛駒出，所以趁熱鬧一齊嚟！（你哋拍拖？）唔係啊，唔好誤會！（有冇買賽事？）買咗一場，輸咗100蚊港紙！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170305/bkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170305%2Fbkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001.html&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcptibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=eb98c9e0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170305/bkn-20170305190747408-0305_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"866ca1adcec44c3eaa46bb020ee32e269acf3fec","tid":144934,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:09:10.000Z","msg":"得個波無樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\